summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 32086, entitled: "An ordinance authorizing and directing the Board of Public Works to purchase the timber on government lots 6, 7 and 8 and the Northeast quarter of the Northeast quarter of section 18; the north half o section 26; north half, Southwest quarter; north half of Southeast quarter of the Southwest quarter of the Southeast quarter of section 28; east half of the east half of section 30, township 22 north, range 9 east, W.M., and providing the method of paying the cost of acquiring the same", approved November 10, 1913.
